title: Week 3 NFL Recap: Russ keeps cooking, Falcons blow another big lead, and our first tie of 2020 (Football 9/28)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech link up to break down all the Sunday action from Week 3 of the 2020 NFL season. 2 quarterback legends met on Sunday Night Football while Russell Wilson displayed once again why he's the early MVP favorite. Somehow, the Eagles and Bengals tied again, while the Falcons were up to their usual tricks. Let's get to the action!
